&lt;p/&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But since a default &lt;tt&gt;RequestConfig&lt;/tt&gt; has been set in &lt;tt&gt;HttpComponentsClientHttpRequestFactory.createRequest&lt;/tt&gt;, it is not applied here and the configured RequestConfig in the HttpClientBuilder is not used.&lt;/p&gt;

